      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="3cfcb21e-b285-4bdb-98a9-30efa8e591ef" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Cân bằng</Vi>
          <En>A state in which opposing forces or influences are balanced, resulting in no net change; stability.</En>
          <Example>The chemical reaction reached equilibrium when the forward and reverse rates became equal.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="01373779-889c-46c1-acd3-daaaf776312b">
              <Vi>Một hệ thống vật lý hoặc hóa học không thay đổi theo thời gian do các lực hoặc quá trình cân bằng nhau.</Vi>
              <En>A physical or chemical system that shows no net change over time because opposing processes are balanced.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="441ae295-981e-4116-9ed3-8cdb62bc7d21">
              <Vi>Tình trạng ổn định trong kinh tế khi tổng cung bằng tổng cầu.</Vi>
              <En>A state of economic stability when aggregate supply equals aggregate demand.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
